{"type": "article", "id": 5963, "title": "挂钟 Tanko", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-06T07:33:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233906DNiFuA7opvc8RXzW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是法国设计师 Jean Louis Iratzoki 为巴斯克大理石品牌 Retegui 设计的一款挂钟 Tanko 。这款挂钟结合了卡拉拉（Carrara）白色大理石的简约特性与全粒面皮革的优雅品质，挂置在墙上时，透出一种温暖的柔软气息。其形状很容易让人联想到煮牛奶时的计时表。Tanko 的皮革部分提供白兰地色、米色以及石墨色 3 种选择，如需购买，请联系 <a href=\"mailto:retegui@aol.com\">retegui@aol.com</a> 。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233905hSA4rEws1UFv0WiD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233905yufVetZsJI8MCG35.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}